ssue and delivered on time.This was achieved only through our team motto \"Try and Try Until You Succeed\".We had committed and delivered projects on time with perseverance even though we had many challenges like new environment, new technologies,time pressure and sometimes requirement change but deadline was the same etc.','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',126,'EGANVIK',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-14 13:20:36','Pending'),('ELOPRTK','prabhat.k.kumar@ericsson.com','Bangalore','EMOHVIJ','BUGS GSI M&A Adaptn ECE CA 3',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,127,'EGANVAI',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-10 14:22:32','Pending'),('ESAAPAI','satyabrata.pani@ericsson.com','Kolkata','EASGAUR','BUGS GSI CSI Central Operations',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,128,'ERANSIR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-11 04:20:52','Pending'),('EPRISAR','priyanka.sarkar@ericsson.com','Kolkata','ECHAARU','BUGS HR Generalist Hub Kolkata',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,129,'EAADMAD',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-11 05:02:07','Pending'),('ESWARNA','swarnapriya.k@ericsson.com','Guindy Chennai','EMOHVIJ','BUGS GSI M&A Adaptn ECE CA 2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,130,'ESUDHMU',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-11 05:05:44','Pending'),('EANIUNN','anitha.unnamalai@ericsson.com','Chennai','ESRISET','BUGS GSI M&A Adaptn TV CA 2','','','','I don’t have much experience in Ericsson to have pursued/experienced all core values yet. I share with you a small experience of mine here. I joined recently in Ericsson in February 2015. When I was given DOJ, it was in January. But due to the commitments I had in my past company I couldn’t join at the time mentioned as DOJ in Ericsson offer. When I contacted Ericsson for DOJ which is almost 35 days after the date that was given by them, they respected my commitment to my previous organization and almost immediately agreed to change my DOJ to