tiple workshop with customer to understand the dump and internally developed the tool to covert the dump into required specified format.\r\n\r\n   And Finally We have completed all the Business configuration in Ericsson Charging system using that Input sheet in very short span of time and successfully migrated the subscribers from Rednee IN system to Ericsson Charging system on same planned date without any delay and It was really called as Flawless migration eventhough we have faced lot of issues in demo migration but solved all the issues before the final migration with our perservance and also very well apreciated by the customer beacuse of the Exceptional performance, team work, perseverance and technical skills demonstrated. One interesting thing after the migration , customer used to call me as champ because the way which i have shown my respect and professionalism with customer.\r\n   \r\nSo Everyone follow the Ericsson Core value ( Prefessionlism,Perseverance and Respect) in personal and professional life. Be a Champion.\r\nThats it about my story. Lets here it from you. Thanks for spending time to read this.','','','','','','',NULL,NULL,221,'ESUDHMU',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-14 05:13:12','Pending'),('EPIYUGU','piyush.d.gupta@ericsson.com','Noida','ENARVAL','BUGS GSI Service Applctn Unit 1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,222,'EGARBHA',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-11 10:42:46','Pending'),('EMQQRTV','s.gobinath@ericsson.com','Kolkata','EBIDMUK','BUGS GSI CS CCN 2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,223,'ESAADAS',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-11 10:45:43','Pending'),('ENQRUVA','ritesh.sharma@ericsson.com','GURGAON','EDHARDH','BUGS GSI CS MINSAT ECMS 1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,224,'ESUJSIH',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-11 10:46:29','Pending'),('ERTVWXP','arunagiri@ericsson.com','Guindy Chennai','EBPBPBP','BUGS GSI CS AIR SDP VS 5',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,