nstrated. Betrayal of any one of those is to lose all three.” \r\n\r\nIt applies for Core Ericsson values - Professionalism is earned by your experience, Respect is given and Perseverance is demonstrated.\r\n\r\nMy journey with Ericsson for past 1.5 years has been wonderful and will be.\r\n\r\nI mean I really experienced so far, hence the journey continues with Ericsson with its values....','','','','','','',NULL,NULL,290,'EPRISAR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-13 06:37:21','Pending'),('ESULNAY','sulatha.nayak@ericsson.com','Bangalore','EDEKALR','BUGS GSI SDT DU IN DDM',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,291,'EANRDAS',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-12 10:42:47','Pending'),('EKUMVKA','v.karthik.kumar@ericsson.com','Chennai','EANISJO','BUGS GSI OSS CM-RNAM Pool-OM4',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,292,'EJALBAN',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-12 10:45:32','Pending'),('ESWIRAJ','swikriti.raj@ericsson.com','PUNE','EDEKATK','BUGS GSI CD-BSS PA Billing 1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,293,'ECHAARU',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-12 11:00:53','Pending'),('ESAKGOP','sakthivel.gopal@ericsson.com','Chennai','ERANANA','BUGS GSI CD-BSS PA CRS',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,294,'EPPPRRR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-12 11:06:11','Pending'),('EMDEKUM','m.deepan.kumar@ericsson.com','Chennai','ESRISET','BUGS GSI M&A Adaptn TV CA 2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,295,'EGANVIK',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-12 11:07:32','Pending'),('ERISHKU','rishav.kumar@ericsson.com','Kolkata','EINDRGH','BUGS GSI OSS CM SA KOL 1','','','','‘Abandon all hope, all ye who enter here.’\r\n\r\nThese words scrawled deep within the recesses of my mind, kept bubbling up each time I looked at the building.Maybe it was the collective, misguided dread of the people around me that made me think so. ‘An IT industry will drain you,’ said one.‘Your life will never be the same again. In fact, you’ll forget what life is like,’a relative grinned as he uttered these words.‘It will devour your soul. IT will devour your soul. Geddit?’ said another.Talk about smart alecs.\r\n\r\nI took a deep breath and walked in.It was my first job, at Ericsson India.\r\n\r\nMy misgivings turned out to be false real soon.Quickly the trainings were done and I was assigned projects.I knew what my job was and what was expected of me.I knew the customers’ demands and the projected deadlines.I understood what it meant to be an IT professional.I realized that it was not just a job, but upholding the integrity and reputation was also my responsibility.I learned what professionalism was.\r\n\r\nThere were times when I was part of projects that were not directly assigned to me.I wholeheartedly participated in them, trying to provide as much help as possible.It was all integral to the job.I reckoned I wasn’t just an individual or an employee of the company,but a part of a family,a team.It was together that we could achieve anything,each with our own individual strengths.The shortcomings could be overcome easily, as there was always someone to give you advice or provide help from time to time. I respected them,and in turn gained theirs.\r\n\r\nI remember an assignment where I had to deliver the project within a very short time.We all worked hard to complete it within the stipulated date.When we saw that we couldn’t,we decided to stay back.For two days at a stretch, we worked continuously,never giving up.In the end, though sleepless and exhausted we were,we had delivered the project on time and that was more refreshing than anything.It was all because we kept pushing forward, because we weren’t satisfied with being just okay.We wanted to be the best, and had already embarked on that journey.\r\n\r\nIt has been more than a year at Ericsson now.I keep getting better.These values are a part of me and keep driving me every day.Sure things get a bit hectic every now and then but what is life without struggle,without a little bit of challenge? I chose this life and I love it.I love being an efficient cog that turns this giant machine.This is what keeps me going.\r\n\r\nThe last lines from the movie The Hurt Locker come to mind:\r\n\r\n‘Once you get older,\r\nsome of the things that you love might not seem so special anymore. \r\nLike your Jack In The Box,\r\nMaybe you realize it\'s just a piece of tin and a stuffed animal \r\nand then you forget the few things you really love, \r\nAnd by the time you get to my age maybe it\'s only one or two things, \r\nWith me I think it\'s one,’\r\n\r\nWelcome to Ericsson.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n','','','','','','',NULL,NULL,296,'EGANVAI',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-18 10:18:33','Pending'),('ESNNDEY','somenath.dey@ericsson.com','Kolkata','EAMPARU','BUGS GSI GITS AD Communication',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,297,'ERANSIR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-12 11:22:18','Pending'),('EJEYSEL','jeyaganesh.selvaraj@ericsson.com','Chennai','EDUTSAN','BUGS GSI BSS EMA-CADE Adaptn 6',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,298,'EAADMAD',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-12 11:31:38','Pending'),('EKODPAV','kodi.y.m.k.pavan@ericsson.com','Chennai','ETHANGA','BUGS GSI CS AIR SDP VS 3','','','','Values provide the foundation for the strategy, the mission and the structure. Values are a set of understandings in our organization about how to work together, how to treat other people and what is most important.\r\nRespect, Professionalism and Perseverenace are essential ingredients in all work environments specially in ericsson. But what does it actually mean to be respectful and professional? Demonstrating respect and professionalism can involve anything from small actions such as saying \"please\" and \"thank you\", to how decisions are communicated within the organization.\r\nWe work to showcase our ericsson core value infront of customer, it i