roject stuff in given timeline.There were few colleagues with less experience, I tried to understand the issues encountering by them and allow them to express their thoughts, ideas and opinions.\r\nAdditionally convinced the senior colleagues to give the junior collegues sufficient time to understand and realise them the situation.\r\nI helped, guided and making them realised  that we need to overcome the issues encountering,bringing their best out of them in quality delivery and get respected.','To be an honest to say for me perseverance is being positive and having patience.\r\nPaience with the adversities that comes while handling projects and customers and positivity is the tool that required.\r\nIn our project customer was looking forward to dismantle one of the product from its Network.\r\nHowever I managed to convinced them having the New product instead of the existing one to meet their current requirements.\r\n\r\nWhile deploying the new product it appears that there are various issues that need to be fixed,however that required considerable amount of time in fixing by the design team, personally continuosly looked upon few product code issues and fixing them temporarily.\r\nAdditionally followed up with Design and support team to work upon the existing issues and fix the same at earliest.\r\nThis has enabled us to make customer convinced and win  customer confidence and trust.\r\nThis is one of the Best core principle of Ericsson that really helped in feeling always positive with pat','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',301,'ESAADAS',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-16 09:57:20','Pending'),('EIMOPPQ','kannan.c.c@ericsson.com','Chennai','ESRISET','BUGS GSI M&A Adaptn TV CA 2',NULL,'I have joined Ericsson on Sep 25th 2014. Here I have learned many technical stuffs and as well as personal interest also. Initially I have been invloved in the small proof of concept project, there I can able to show my technical talent in the GUI part. As part of personal interest, I have showcased my talent of solving Rubix Cube in Confluence 2.0. I solved the 3x3 Rubix cube in 39 seconds. For these things I have been appreciated from my managers and my colleagues. I am very much impressed with the Ericsson values(especially RESPECT). ',NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',302,'ESUJSIH',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-15 10:29:37','Pending'),('EXABCER','manish.q.kumar@ericsson.com','GURGAON','EGGADDK','BUGS GSI CD-BSS Engagement 2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,303,'EPRISAR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-12 12:55:41','Pending'),('EFFGJJL','prabhakaran.m@ericsson.com','Chennai','EARSIVA','BUGS GSI MS Cricket-ITOC',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,304,'EANRDAS',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-12 18:26:09','Pending'),('EFGJKKM','karthikeyan.k@ericsson.com','Chennai','EARSIVA','BUGS GSI MS Cricket-ITOC','Work Culture is very good in Ericsson, enjoying the whole crew. Hospitality, ambience is awesome. Enjoying working here.','I should appraciate the HR policies here, it completely supports the employees welfare. Also with the higher level management, whenever we raise a conern it is addressed as soon as they can.','Key to success is all about trainings, that is happening well in EGI. L&D is organizing all sort of techinal trainings which helps us out to acheive in our carrier as well as to support the growth of EGI','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',305,'EJALBAN',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-13 05:00:11','Pending'),('ETYAANK','ankur.tyagi@ericsson.com','Noida','EASGAUR','BUGS GSI CSI Central Operations','','','','\r\nPotential learners, skilled workforce, respect for work along with the focus on personal and professional growth are the key aspects that define Ericsson and its people. Ericsson, no doubt is a great place to begin a career if one wants to learn a lot and is looking for global exposure. \r\nWorking here is indeed an excellent experience. It’s not