e - a KEY to SUCCESS!    *-*-*-*-*-*-*-*\r\n\r\nBeing part of Ericsson, all of us are always involved in projects. And projects always involve budget, deadlines, quality, issues etc.\r\nI’ve been part of several projects in my Ericsson journey but there has been a time when I did my first project for MTN-Guinea. It was mix of on-site & offshore project. As it was my first project, I had little understanding of our product.\r\nWhile I was working from offshore, customer was not able to login to one of the CCNs. Even I tried several things but nothing worked out and the resolution to this issue was getting delayed with customer escalations.\r\nFinally the moment came when I went onsite. There I did troubleshooting once again for the same CCN issue although I never worked on CCN and despite the fact that it was my first project.\r\nAt the last I found that the problem was with a parameter in sshd_config file. I logged in through console, fixed the issue and confirmed back to customer regarding issue fixation. Customer tested the solution provided and was quite happy as no one was able to fix the issue.\r\nAll of this happened by simply following Ericsson’s values Professionalism (Which I showed to customer by taking him into confidence that we can solve the issue), Respect (That we always give to everyone) and specially Perseverance which simply means, in my views, “Dedication & firm determination towards anything can make you FLY WITH COLORS irrespective of whether you’re experienced or new to it.”\r\nThis way, Ericsson values have helped me in my professional life and personal life as well.','','','','','','',NULL,NULL,308,'EGANVIK',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-18 08:01:52','Pending'),('ECPBALA','c.p.balamurugan@ericsson.com','Chennai','ESHAHHA','BUGS GSI CS AIR SDP VS 1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,309,'EGANVAI',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-13 05:34:41','Pending'),('ESUGAVA','sugavanan.v@ericsson.com','Guindy Chennai','EMAPA