ing. I have observed all my colleagues living these values and working with various stakeholders has helped me understand how these values are followed in our work.\r\nI would like to share one story here that happened 6-7 months ago where we had a requirement from our region for a document to be sent to customer by end of day. This was not a standard document and it required updates from many people and one resource was sick with a very high fever.She was a very key resource and we had aligned a back-up however considering the severity, she updated the document despite her medical condition. Post her updates, we completed the remaining updates, reviewed the document and finished up the work by 11:30PM IST such that the customer based in RASO could get their document by next day morning. This activity helped cement our place with the region and until now we have been able to have a steady working relationship with them due to the trust that was built on that day 6 months ago.\r\nI have seen all the 3 values in this experience - Professionalism shown by the resource, Respect to the customer and one another and Perseverance shown by the entire team. This definitely helped us in the long run and these are the values we live with till this day.','','','','','','','EFABIJO/EUYYZBD_All_1932591892.mp4','Living the Ericsson Values every day.',313,'EGARBHA',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-15 10:14:39','Completed'),('EPRIYNE','priyanka.negi@ericsson.com','Chennai','EKATHRA','BUGS GSI IP & Core-UDM',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,314,'ESAADAS',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-13 07:18:22','Pending'),('ENRSTAA','nagabhushana.m.l@ericsson.com','Bangalore','ETHANGA','BUGS GSI CS AIR SDP VS 3','Professionalism captures what it means to be a professional, and what is expected of them. In Ericsson we pay attention to the cultural norms and  follow them by respecting in all work we do.Be pleasant and polite to people, even if you don\'t like them even 