nd ethical behavior in the workplace can benefit your career and improve your working environment. If Professionalism is well maintained, ultimately you can get Respect and Persistence in doing project works despite difficulty or delay in achieving success...not only for your personal life but also for the organization you are working with.”','','','','','','',NULL,NULL,324,'EAADMAD',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-13 10:49:32','Pending'),('ERSUVVX','harish.d.kumar@ericsson.com','GURGAON','ERRNSSR','BUGS GSI PDU ACNT 1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,325,'ESUDHMU',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-13 08:43:02','Pending'),('ETUSRAI','tushar.rai@ericsson.com','Gurgaon','ESONABH','BUGS GSI EMA 2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,326,'EGARBHA',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-13 08:48:57','Pending'),('EGHKKMD','shreya.b@ericsson.com','Bangalore','EGANVAI','BUGS GSI OSS Adaptation','','','','Its been 5 months i have joined Ericsson .  Proud to be a part of Ericsson Family . Its my pleasure to learn the Ericsson values  .  Its been 2 months i got my Project and then i experienced the Ericsson values  . Our project Team has a status delivery meeting for 1 hour every week. And there everyone had to be present on the meeting on time. The meeting request should be accepted with a response  as soon as we recieve it . Coming to the second value, Respect. There is a saying \'Give Respect and Take Respect\' .And i experinced it here . Being helpful in your collegues critical situations helps u in ur critical situations . And the last one Perseverance, taking work with dedication helps to build the perseverance . Once i had to leave early around 3, i had to completed some work by EOD. And i completed it before i left office. The happiness u get once u complete your work on time is unexplainable.','','','','','','',NULL,NULL,327,'ESAADAS',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-13 13:14:36','Pending'),('EMAAMAL','maria.amalraj@er