ect : It is easier to manage people by providing a single set of rules to follow. But this limits our creativity. Because as an individual, we all are different with our our own taste and comfort zone. Ericsson treats its employees as an individual. We are given the freedom to express ourselves in our own way. As a result we are not purely a dull set of gray and white. Rather we collectively represent a wide spectrum of vibrant colors.\r\n\r\nPerseverance : Trying new idea is one thing. Sticking to it and delivering good result everyday is different. People say being casual is a slow process of giving up. But here we prove it wrong everyday. Defying the contemporary is the way of life here. No giving up until we get the job done. This is the ericsson way living.','','','','','','',NULL,NULL,385,'EPPPRRR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-14 10:49:49','Pending'),('EADIDAS','aditi.das@ericsson.com','KOLKATA','ESHLSIE','BUGS GSI Sprint Fac',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,386,'EGANVIK',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-14 08:31:46','Pending'),('EPUJCHA','puja.chakroborty@ericsson.com','Kolkata','ERUPSAR','BUGS GSI ADM&ADC&JOSP&JOSP C',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,387,'EGANVAI',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-14 08:33:22','Pending'),('EAKHMDF','md.firoz.akhtar@ericsson.com','Kolkata','EKAUSRO','BUGS GSI BA Presales',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,388,'ERANSIR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-14 08:34:09','Pending'),('EDIBNAT','DibyaRanjan.Nath@ericsson.com','Kolkata','ECHASAP','BUGS GSI E2E Architecture Group 1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,389,'EAADMAD',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015-05-14 08:36:31','Pending'),('EASHWMV','ashwini.mv@ericsson.com','Bangalore','ESULNAY','BUGS GSI SDT DU IN DDM1',NULL,NULL,'Perseverance to achieve the unachievable...\r\n\r\nI would like to share what perseverance means for me, it means to pursue consistently, especial